casebody.data:
Tuesday, August 5, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

96-2247. State ex rel. The Plain Dealer v. Ohio Dept. of Ins.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus.

Upon consideration of relators’ motion to amend entry of July 16,1997,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, J., dissents.
